// 
// NETR       Operation 1 of 8
// Local PLC Data Table        Remote PLC = 2    Operation Status
//  VB0 - VB0              <---   VB0 - VB0           NETR1_Status:VB243
// Data Length: 1 byte(s)
// 
// NETW       Operation 2 of 8
// Local PLC Data Table        Remote PLC = 2    Operation Status
//  VB1 - VB1              --->   VB1 - VB1           NETW2_Status:VB251
// Data Length: 1 byte(s)
// 
// NETR       Operation 3 of 8
// Local PLC Data Table        Remote PLC = 4    Operation Status
//  VB2 - VB2              <---   VB0 - VB0           NETR3_Status:VB259
// Data Length: 1 byte(s)
